labor_categories.labor_category: Subject Matter Expert – Cloud Computing I

raw_data.title: Subject Matter Expert – Cloud Computing I
raw_data.description: This role is responsible for leading the creation of a cloud technology framework and providing cloud technical leadership. The Architect will institute processes to build and assess which applications will access cloud computing and which will be on-premise and design the hybrid cloud environment inclusive of all security related designs. Identify any comprehensive risks and come up with risk-mitigation mapping matrix. Cloud Migration.  Application rationalization and migration priorities would be one of key responsibilities of this role. Rationalization involves determining which legacy systems can be sunset in order to avoid costly unwanted cloud migration efforts. Prioritization involves determining order of the move based on various criteria such as hardware lifecycle, security requirements, sunsetting legacy applications, need for application modernization etc. Should have good project management skills and ability to articulate cloud topics with senior management to secure their confidence.
